  "instructions": [
    "Whisk the egg yolks and vegetable stock together until smooth.",
    "Add soy sauce, mirin, water, and salt; stir until dissolved.",
    "Fold in chopped coriander, carrot, and green onion.",
    "Strain the mixture through a fine sieve into heat‑proof ramekins.",
    "Cover the ramekins with foil and steam over simmering water for 10 minutes.",
    "Remove the ramekins and place them in a bowl of ice water to chill for 5 minutes.",
    "Drain and dust with sesame seeds before serving."
